headline: M&T Bank Unveils 'Team M&T' to Power Its Sports Marketing Strategy
summary: M&T Bank (NYSE:MTB) today announced the launch of Team M&T, a new sponsorship initiative that highlights the power of individual athletes and their impact on and off the field. Team M&T goes beyond traditional team sponsorships to support athletes as leaders, advocates and role models.
